headline: 4 Accident & Health Insurance Stocks to Watch as Exposure Increases
summary: Lower claims frequency, moderate pricing and the adoption of technology are likely to boost the performance of Zacks Accident and Health Insurance industry players like AFL, UNM, TRUP and EIG.
